<article class="teaser teaser-lg blog-entry--teaser" data-nid="5018772">

  <div class="teaser-lg--main">

          <div class="teaser-lg__image">
        
              <a href="/us/blog/the-superhuman-mind/202404/4-surprising-ways-ai-poses-a-threat-to-humanity"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_1_1_288x288/public/teaser_image/blog_entry/2024-04/Hacked%20pic%20pexels-saksham-choudhary-2036656.jpg?itok=l6lSeYDH" width="288" height="288" alt="" title="Saksham Choudhary/Pexels" />

</a>

      
      </div>
    
    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/the-superhuman-mind/202404/4-surprising-ways-ai-poses-a-threat-to-humanity" rel="bookmark">4 Surprising Ways AI Poses a Threat to Humanity</a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            AI can become capable of waging psychological warfare, sabotaging companies, and changing world power.  
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            AI can become capable of waging psychological warfare, sabotaging companies, and changing world power.  
      </p>
  </article>
</div>
    <div class="teaser-listing-item">




<article class="teaser teaser-lg blog-entry--teaser" data-nid="5018485">

  <div class="teaser-lg--main">

          <div class="teaser-lg__image">
        
              <a href="/us/blog/peaceful-parenting/202403/3-ways-to-tell-when-a-narcissist-is-lying"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_1_1_288x288/public/teaser_image/blog_entry/2024-03/AE4FD82E-86F6-469C-B924-35021D942541.jpg?itok=vL3kDfhE" width="288" height="288" alt="" title="Vika Glitter / Pexels" />

</a>

      
      </div>
    
    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/peaceful-parenting/202403/3-ways-to-tell-when-a-narcissist-is-lying" rel="bookmark">3 Ways to Tell When a Narcissist Is Lying </a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            When you see a narcissist rapidly move through denial, blame-shifting, and shutting down the conversation, it&#039;s a red flag they might be lying.
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            When you see a narcissist rapidly move through denial, blame-shifting, and shutting down the conversation, it&#039;s a red flag they might be lying.
      </p>
  </article>
</div>
    <div class="teaser-listing-item">




