    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/the-human-equation/202403/deceived-and-manipulated-by-a-fake-mental-illness" rel="bookmark">Deceived and Manipulated by a Fake Mental Illness</a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            Movies like &quot;Split&quot; sacrifice truth for drama, relying on negative stereotypes about violence and mental illness. Here&#039;s how one predator used this to his advantage. 
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            Movies like &quot;Split&quot; sacrifice truth for drama, relying on negative stereotypes about violence and mental illness. Here&#039;s how one predator used this to his advantage. 
      </p>
  </article>
