    <div class="teaser-lg__details">
      
                        <div class="h2 teaser-lg__title">
            <a href="/us/blog/what-is-a-human/202403/the-trouble-with-mirrors" rel="bookmark">Why Mirrors May Not Show Our &quot;Real&quot; Selves</a>
          </div>
              
      
              <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--desktop">
            We are not satisfied with mirrors because they do not show our ‘real’ selves, but there is no true self, only the result of an ongoing negotiation with ourselves.
      </p>
          </div>

  </div>

      <p class="teaser-lg__summary teaser-lg__teaser--mobile">
            We are not satisfied with mirrors because they do not show our ‘real’ selves, but there is no true self, only the result of an ongoing negotiation with ourselves.
